The privileges of the University of Oxford in point of visitation cleerly evidenced by letter to an honourable personage : together with the university's answer to the summons of the visitors. Fell, John, 1625-1686. Waring, Robert, 1614-1658. Allestree, Richard, 1619-1681. Langbaine, Gerard, 1609-1658.

s.n.], [London : MDCXLVII [1647]
Authorship of this work has been claimed by Robert Waring and variously attributed to John Fell, Richard Allestree and Gerard Langbaine -- cf. Madan, Falconer. Oxford books, v. 2, p. 459. Reproduction of the original in the Harvard University Library.
